DocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 30, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rgc1665703134402.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rgc1665703134402.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rgc1665703134402.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rgc1665703134402\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__uglabdbm_404387\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get a list of all the model entities in the component.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__topic_d121121e1_d121122e1_d121123e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rgc1665703134402_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__codeblock_zpt_1y1_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">short uglabdbm (unsigned char*Buffer);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__topic_d86007e1_d86008e1_d86009e1_d86010e1_d86011e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1066606e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__parml_v4v_by1_1wb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Buffer</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">(Output) The comma-separated list of entities. This buffer must be large enough\n                  to contain the data.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__topic_d86012e1_d86013e1_d86014e1_d86015e1_d86016e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1066606e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__p_d121136e1_d121137e1_d121138e1\">0—this function always returns zero.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__topic_d86017e1_d86018e1_d86019e1_d86020e1_d86021e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1066606e89\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__topic_d86022e1_d86023e1_d86024e1_d86025e1_d86026e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1066606e102\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__p_d121148e1_d121149e1_d121150e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uglabdbm</code> gets the names of all the\n            model entities in the calling component, and places them in <var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var>,\n            separated by commas. The buffer will be zero-terminated. Entities that are painted only\n            on the component, but not defined in the application model (so-called ‘dummy entities’),\n            are not included in the list.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__note_N10072_N1005E_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> This function, unlike most functions that get data, does not have a<var class=\"keyword varname\">max</var>parameter to specify the maximum number of bytes returned. You must ensure that your buffer is large enough to hold all the names. If not, your application is likely to crash.</div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example prints the list of model entities in the component\n            to the message frame. (The size of 2000 bytes for the buffer is arbitrary, but will\n            probably be enough in most cases).</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rgc1665703134402_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rgc1665703134402__codeblock_mnn_2y1_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT void GETENTNAMES ()\n{\nchar buf[2000];\nuglabdbm(buf);\nu_printf(\"Model entities in the component are : %s\\n:, buf);\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ysz1665703132557.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uflabdbm</a><p>Get a list of the names of all database fields in an entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531579\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531579\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uglabdbm Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 30, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get a list of all the model entities in the component. Explain this code short uglabdbm (unsigned char*Buffer); Copy Parameters Buffer (Output) The comma-separated list of entities. This buffer must be large enough to contain the data. Return Values 0—this function always returns zero. Use Library: yrtl Description uglabdbm gets the names of all the model entities in the calling component, and places them in buffer , separated by commas. The buffer will be zero-terminated. Entities that are painted only on the component, but not defined in the application model (so-called ‘dummy entities’), are not included in the list. CAUTION: This function, unlike most functions that get data, does not have a max parameter to specify the maximum number of bytes returned. You must ensure that your buffer is large enough to hold all the names. If not, your application is likely to crash. The following example prints the list of model entities in the component to the message frame. (The size of 2000 bytes for the buffer is arbitrary, but will probably be enough in most cases). Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void GETENTNAMES () { char buf[2000]; uglabdbm(buf); u_printf(\"Model entities in the component are : %s\\n:, buf); } Copy Related Links uflabdbm Get a list of the names of all database fields in an entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}